about: Hello, I am Manny I may be a normal person. BUT I am actually not, I am annoying sometimes but I think I am not annoying anymore yeah. I get banned from servers a lot but this one I didn't so  I decided to play it. Then I got used to it and made friends! Not everyone knows me on the server, and not everyone wants to waste their time talking to me :'(. I try to act as friendly as possible, but if you cross the line I will act up SO YOU BETTER NOT. I want everyone to know me on the server so far not everyone does... and I don't think the mods won't be my friends any time soon :(.  Also I may only have one friend right now but I actually have some I just don't want to waste their time going on the website just to friend me. So yeah SEE YA ON THE SERVER HOPEFULLY! :D
